HEADWORD: Galatian
<hw>Ga*la"tian</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to Galatia or its inhabitants. -- A native or inhabitant of
Galatia, in Asia Minor; a descendant of the Gauls who settled in Asia
Minor.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

